snippet: Devon Hall's offense is coming around after a slow start to the season, and on a Virginia team that lacks a go-to scorer, it's an important development as the 13th-ranked Cavaliers head into the more challenging part of their schedule....
lead_paragraph: Devon Hall's offense is coming around after a slow start to the season, and on a Virginia team that lacks a go-to scorer, it's an important development as the 13th-ranked Cavaliers head into the more challenging part of their schedule.

headline.main: Hall Leads No. 13 Virginia Past Robert Morris, 79-39
